Summary of items regarding teacher assignments for
this year:

1) There will be three full time Kindergarden classes,
with three full teachers.

2) Mrs. Kidd will return to her assistant principal
job, there will be a full time teacher for that class.

3) The teacher who was volunteering her time for,
sorry, I forget which class, will now be hired for
that class.

4) Mrs. Williams will be the permanent teacher for the
4th grade options class.

5) There will not be any split classes in the school.

I hope that this conveys the information that we were
given, with the sense that there will be little
disruption from the instruction and relationships
already formed these first few weeks.  I expect that
formal notices and information will be coming out too,
but I know that if I hadn't been able to attend the
meeting I would have wanted to here something quickly.
I think I got it right, but any mistakes in this
message are solely my responsibility!

Ann

